00:09:47,585 --> 00:09:48,629
D'accord ?

181
00:09:49,536 --> 00:09:50,839
Je suis avec toi.

182
00:09:51,219 --> 00:09:52,216
Maintenant.

183
00:09:53,224 --> 00:09:55,677
- Car je t'ai expliqué.
- Qu'est-ce que...

184
00:09:57,605 --> 00:09:58,405
Voilà.

185
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:06,085
Merde.

186
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,758
- Il a dit ça ?
- Mon Dieu !

187
00:10:08,993 --> 00:10:11,694
Quelle incroyable surprise !

188
00:10:11,944 --> 00:10:13,578
