00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,676
Mais c'est Barney.

201
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,018
Je dois lui dire non.

202
00:10:48,185 --> 00:10:50,230
Bon sang, tu vas lui briser le...

