223
00:11:49,114 --> 00:11:49,916
Et...

224
00:11:50,686 --> 00:11:51,686
excuse-moi.

225
00:11:54,129 --> 00:11:56,379
T'es vraiment jolie,
mais anormalement grande

226
00:11:56,546 --> 00:11:58,192
